These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-1-1::.
There 7 different types of food: orange, kiwi, papaya, nectarine, pomegranate, apricot, eggplant
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: skateboarding, weightlifting, baseball, water-polo, swimming, rowing, surfing
The people use 7 different means of transport: tram, jet-ski, roller, boat, bus, bike, scooter
 1. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far right##1
 3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
 5. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
 6. the person eating papaya is the person driving the roller##1
 7. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 8. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
 9. the person driving the roller is the person who's sport is baseball##1
10. the person driving the boat is the person eating pomegranate##1
11. the person eating orange is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
12. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
13. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
14. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
15. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |     3     |     4     |      5       |     6      |     7      |
| Food        | nectarine | papaya     | apricot | kiwi | orange      | eggplant | pomegranate       |
| Sport       | weightlifting        | baseball   | skateboarding   | surfing    | rowing | water-polo    | swimming     |
| Transport   | tram    | roller | scooter       | bike     | jet-ski   | bus     | boat |

