.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-1-2::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: lemonade, almond-milk, tea, mirinda, juice, water, hot-chocolate
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: adventure, crime, epic, sports, superhero, musical, documentary
7 different pets are kept: goat, ferret, pony, goldfish, snake, guinea-pig, chinchilla
 1. the person drinking tea is the person watching sports movies##1
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
 3. the person watching superhero movies is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 4. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 5. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
 6. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 7. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 8. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 9. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
10. the person watching documentary movies is the owner of the goldfish##1
11. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
12. the owner of the ferret is the person drinking water##1
13. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person drinking lemonade##1
14. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
15. the person watching crime movies is on the far right##1
16. the person watching adventure movies is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |     4     |   5    |   6    |   7    |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate  | lemonade     | mirinda  | juice  | tea   | almond-milk | water   |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | superhero | documentary | adventure | sports | musical | crime |
| Pet           | pony    | guinea-pig   | goldfish  | chinchilla    | snake | goat   | ferret    |

