.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-1-3::.
There 7 different types of food: mango, kiwi, lettuce, plum, potato, broccoli, kale
7 different pets are kept: hedgehog, goldfish, guinea-pig, hamster, mouse, frog, rat
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: lacrosse, badminton, soccer, tennis, surfing, volleyball, handball
 1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person eating plum##1
 2. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the owner of the rat is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left##1
 6. the person eating mango is on the right of the person eating plum##1
 7. the owner of the hamster is on the far right##1
 8. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person eating mango##1
 9. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
11. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
12. the person eating plum is in the middle##1
13. the person eating kale is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
14. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
15. the person who's sport is tennis is in the middle##1
16. the owner of the hedgehog is the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |   4   |     5      |    6    |     7      |
| Food    | potato | lettuce | kale | plum | mango      | kiwi | broccoli |
| Pet     | hedgehog         | rat     | guinea-pig   | mouse | goldfish        | frog  | hamster       |
| Sport   | badminton    | volleyball     | handball  | tennis  | lacrosse | surfing  | soccer   |

