 3. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person eating onion##1
 4. the person eating potato is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
 5. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 6. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 7. the person eating blueberry is in the middle##1
 8. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 9. the person who's sport is baseball is the person watching animation movies##1
10. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far right##1
11. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person eating blueberry##1
12. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
13. the person eating lime is the person watching fantasy movies##1
14. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person eating lime##1
15. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
