 5. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person watching horror movies##1
 8. the person watching crime movies is the person who's hobby is reading##1
 9. the person who's hobby is writing is the person watching drama movies##1
10. the person watching thriller movies is in the middle##1
11. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
12. the person watching drama movies is the person who's hobby is writing##1
13. the person who's hobby is rabbiting is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
14. the person who's hobby is writing is the owner of the hedgehog##1
15. the person who's hobby is rabbiting is the owner of the ferret##1
