 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 5. the accountant is in the middle##1
 6. the fan of ambient is on the left of the firefighter##1
 7. the person who's hobby is hiking is the architect##1
 8. the fan of r&b is the librarian##1
 9. the firefighter is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
10. the fan of techno is on the right of the dancer##1
11. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the dancer##1
12. the fisherman is on the left of the firefighter##1
13. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
14. the librarian is on the left of the dancer##1
15. the person who's hobby is card-games is the fisherman##1
16. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

