.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-1-16::.
There 7 different types of food: kale, garlic, asparagus, grapefruit, pear, mango, banana
The people have 7 different jobs:  lawyer, architect, analyst, nurse, designer, social-worker, project-manager
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: superhero, action, western, disaster, romance, sports, martial-arts
 1. the lawyer is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
 2. the person eating garlic is on the right of the lawyer##1
 3. the nurse is on the left of the architect##1
 4. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
 5. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person eating mango##1
 6. the analyst is the person watching sports movies##1
 7. the analyst is on the left of the designer##1
 8. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left##1
 9. the person watching action movies is on the right of the analyst##1
10. the person eating banana is the nurse##1
11. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the nurse##1
12. the person eating pear is in the middle##1
13. the person eating asparagus is the person watching disaster movies##1
14. the person watching sports movies is the person eating kale##1
15. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
16. the project-manager is on the right of the person eating mango##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |     4     |      5      |      6      |     7      |
| Food          | mango    | garlic | kale  | pear | grapefruit | banana     | asparagus    |
| Job           | lawyer    | project-manager  | analyst | designer | social-worker       | nurse    | architect |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | western  | sports      | action | romance      | martial-arts | disaster    |

