.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-1-17::.
There 7 different types of food: artichoke, nectarine, cranberry, banana, grapefruit, mango, peach
The people have 7 different jobs:  pilot, architect, videographer, dressmaker, teacher, accountant, lawyer
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: snowboarding, biathlon, surfing, rugby, baseball, weightlifting, cycling
 1. the dressmaker is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the accountant##1
 3. the accountant is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in the middle##1
 5. the dressmaker is in the middle##1
 6. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
 7. the videographer is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
 8. the person eating banana is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 9. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
10. the person eating mango is the person who's sport is surfing##1
11. the architect is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
12. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
13. the person eating mango is on the left of the teacher##1
14. the person eating banana is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
15. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the accountant##1
16. the lawyer is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |      3      |     4      |      5       |      6      |     7     |
| Food    | mango | nectarine  | artichoke       | peach | banana    | grapefruit | cranberry     |
| Job     | architect     | teacher | videographer | dressmaker | lawyer | pilot   | accountant     |
| Sport   | surfing   | baseball    | rugby  | weightlifting     | biathlon   | cycling  | snowboarding |

