 1. the nurse is in the middle##1
 2. the paramedic is on the right of the fan of rock##1
 3. the bartender is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 4. the fan of reggae is on the far left##1
 5. the fan of pop is on the right of the nurse##1
 6. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
 7. the fan of funk is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 8. the engineer is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
 9. the electrician is on the left of the librarian##1
10. the scientist is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
11. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far right##1
12. the fan of country is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
13. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the nurse##1
14. the fan of house is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
15. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
16. the electrician is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1

