7 different pets are kept: goat, pony, horse, goldfish, rabbit, ferret, hedgehog
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: snowboarding, climbing, badminton, golf, tennis, biathlon, cricket
 1. the person who's sport is biathlon is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 2. the videographer is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 3. the manager is on the far left##1
 4. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 5. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the police-officer##1
 6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
 7. the person who's sport is badminton is the owner of the rabbit##1
 8. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the musician##1
 9. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
10. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
11. the videographer is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
12. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
13. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the manager##1
14. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the photographer##1
15. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2        |     3     |     4      |    5     |     6      |     7      |
| Job     | manager   | police-officer | musician | photographer  | videographer     | doctor      | accountant |
| Pet     | goat        | ferret          | horse      | goldfish | hedgehog    | pony | rabbit    |
| Sport   | cricket | tennis         | climbing  | snowboarding | biathlon | golf      | badminton     |

