.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-1-20::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, mirinda, 7up, almond-milk, milk, juice
There are 7 different nationalities: french, american, brazilian, russian, polish, nigerian, pakistani
The people use 7 different means of transport: tram, helicopter, roller, trike, subway, jet-ski, scooter
 1. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the nigerian##1
 2. the french is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 3. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 4. the american is on the far right##1
 5. the brazilian is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
 7. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 8. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 9. the polish is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
10. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
11. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
12. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the brazilian##1
13. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the polish##1
14. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
15. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far right##1
16. the person drinking juice is the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3     |     4      |     5     |     6      |     7      |
| Beverage      | 7up | mirinda | hot-chocolate     | coffee       | juice       | milk     | almond-milk   |
| Nationality   | polish   | russian  | french | nigerian   | pakistani | brazilian    | american |
| Transport     | scooter    | tram     | roller | subway | helicopter       | trike | jet-ski       |

 